16
00:00:49,200 --> 00:00:50,270
How do they do it?

17
00:00:50,440 --> 00:00:52,910
Iceland is a country
with many mountains and rivers.

18
00:00:53,080 --> 00:00:58,710
As a result, they produce 73% of
their electricity with hydropower plants.

19
00:00:58,880 --> 00:01:01,870
To create electricity,
it's always the same thing.

20
